➜双十一活动打响，打工人的钱包要哭了
https://www.uisdc.com/c4d-class-12-2020	57667
<p>一年一度的双11又来了，你全身上下最贵的车装满了吗？</p>
<p>在普通消费者眼里，双11可能仅仅只是一场购物狂欢，但在设计师眼中，双十一可是一场精彩绝伦的视觉盛宴！</p>
<p>今年天猫也是如约而至地联合各大品牌，发布了一幅又一幅创意满满的「猫头海报」，其中，C4D作品可是占据了绝大多数：</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="双十一活动打响，打工人的钱包要哭了" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-394575" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/c4d-class-12-20201102-1.jpg" width="690" height="345" /></span> <span class="img-zoom"><img alt="双十一活动打响，打工人的钱包要哭了" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-394576" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/c4d-class-12-20201102-2.jpg" width="690" height="345" /></span> <span class="img-zoom"><img alt="双十一活动打响，打工人的钱包要哭了" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-394577" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/c4d-class-12-20201102-3.jpg" width="690" height="345" /></span> <span class="img-zoom"><img alt="双十一活动打响，打工人的钱包要哭了" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-394578" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/c4d-class-12-20201102-4.jpg" width="690" height="345" /></span> <span class="img-zoom"><img alt="双十一活动打响，打工人的钱包要哭了" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-394579" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/c4d-class-12-20201102-5.jpg" width="690" height="345" /></span> <span class="img-zoom"><img alt="双十一活动打响，打工人的钱包要哭了" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-394580" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/c4d-class-12-20201102-6.jpg" width="690" height="345" /></span> <span class="img-zoom"><img alt="双十一活动打响，打工人的钱包要哭了" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-394581" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/c4d-class-12-20201102-7.jpg" width="690" height="345" /></span> <span class="img-zoom"><img alt="双十一活动打响，打工人的钱包要哭了" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-394582" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/c4d-class-12-20201102-8.jpg" width="690" height="345" /></span> <span class="img-zoom"><img alt="双十一活动打响，打工人的钱包要哭了" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-394583" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/c4d-class-12-20201102-9.jpg" width="690" height="345" /></span></p>
<p>不得不说，层出不穷的优秀3D作品实在是太养眼了，就算兜里的钱包早已哭泣，也愿意戳进海报里一探究竟。</p>
<p>除了猫头海报系列，许多店铺页、闪屏海报中，C4D作品也是出尽了风头，排面满满~</p>
<p>其中优设C4D特训班最近也出现了一大波优秀双11海报，着实惊艳到我了，精美程度毫不逊色于各大品牌的官方作品：</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="双十一活动打响，打工人的钱包要哭了" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-394584" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/c4d-class-12-20201102-10.jpg" width="750" height="1333" /></span></p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="双十一活动打响，打工人的钱包要哭了" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-394585" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/c4d-class-12-20201102-11.jpg" width="750" height="719" /></span></p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="双十一活动打响，打工人的钱包要哭了" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-394586" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/c4d-class-12-20201102-12.jpg" width="750" height="665" /></span></p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="双十一活动打响，打工人的钱包要哭了" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-394587" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/c4d-class-12-20201102-13.jpg" width="750" height="665" /></span></p>
<p>对于设计师来讲，双11的视觉盛宴，几乎可以约等于一场优秀3D作品秀了。</p>
<p>那么，究竟为什么C4D会这么火爆呢？</p>
<p>或许很多人觉得，自己平面技能都半斤八两，3D技能岂不是难到登天？其实并非如此，大量设计师将C4D技能纳入囊中，自然是得益于它友好简洁的操作。一些大神前辈的强大预设库，更是能让你的作品如虎添翼~</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="双十一活动打响，打工人的钱包要哭了" class="alignnone wp-image-394589 size-full" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/c4d-class-12-20201102-14-e1604315150921.jpg" width="300" height="304" /></span></p>
<p>在各式各样的3D设计软件中，C4D可是名副其实的优等生。强大的渲染器，其他软件追不上的渲染速度和渲染质量，与PS，AI，AE等软件都可以轻松做到无缝结合……数不清的优点，让C4D在各行各业中都备受宠爱。</p>
<p>比如我们在各种海报中见到的产品素材，常常就是通过建模来呈现的。还原真实感的同时，还能够更方便地增加艺术效果，规避版权风险：</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="双十一活动打响，打工人的钱包要哭了" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-394590" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/c4d-class-12-20201102-15.jpg" width="750" height="420" /></span></p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="双十一活动打响，打工人的钱包要哭了" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-394591" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/c4d-class-12-20201102-16.jpg" width="750" height="421" /></span></p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="双十一活动打响，打工人的钱包要哭了" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-394592" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/c4d-class-12-20201102-17.jpg" width="750" height="421" /></span></p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="双十一活动打响，打工人的钱包要哭了" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-394593" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/c4d-class-12-20201102-18.jpg" width="750" height="421" /></span></p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="双十一活动打响，打工人的钱包要哭了" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-394594" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/c4d-class-12-20201102-19.jpg" width="750" height="421" /></span></p>
<p>△优设C4D实战班学员作业</p>
<p>随着C4D的风靡，越来越多的闪屏海报中也出现了C4D的身影，比如下面这些节日节气闪屏，视觉吸引力提升了好几个Level！</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="双十一活动打响，打工人的钱包要哭了" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-394595" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/c4d-class-12-20201102-20.jpg" width="750" height="1500" /></span></p>
