<p>以及我们熟悉的京东，也跟丁汀老师有过合作：</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="双十一活动打响，打工人的钱包要哭了" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-394620" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/c4d-class-12-20201102-45.gif" width="500" height="250" /></span></p>
